      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Open Source framework and it been built by microsoft\n\n- Enables that AI Agent to converse each other to solve the task\n\n- Instead of fixed workflow graph, you built chat based orchestration\n\n- Workflows will intreact as dialogues within the agents \n\n- Agents will have access to tools/ LLm / human input , they exchange message, \ninvoke tools and ask questions\n\n- Enables, flexible dynamic way of solving the problem through natural language",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Open Source framework and it been built by microsoft\n\n- Enables that AI Agent to converse each other to solve the task\n\n- Instead of fixed workflow graph, you built chat based orchestration\n\n- Workflows will intreact as dialogues within the agents \n\n- Agents will have access to tools/ LLm / human input , they exchange message, \ninvoke tools and ask questions\n\n- Enables, flexible dynamic way of solving the problem through natural language",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
